ername, Password) بشكل صحيح لتشغيل القنوات بدون أخطاء على مختلف الأجهزة.\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"flex justify-center my-6\">\n            <div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[320px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 bg-black\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;\">\n                <iframe \n                    class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full border-0\"\n                    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9SYHAGKzXg0\"\n                    title=\"طريقة اضافة حساب أكستريم\"\n                    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n                    allowfullscreen>\n                </iframe>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-blue-100 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-3xl p-7 my-8 shadow-inner\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\">\n            <span class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl shadow-md text-xl flex-shrink-0\">\n                <svg class=\"w-7 h-7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>\n            </span>\n            <h3 class=\"font-bold text-2xl text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 m-0\">يسمح لك بمشاهدة المحتوى حسب الطلب (VOD):</h3>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"mb-5\">\n            <ul class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 list-none p-0 m-0\">\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 text-xl\">•</span> رياضه بث مباشر</li>\n                <l